snippet.textDisplay: I killed Amir Zaki.. You killed Amir.. Yes we all killed him by our attitude to ignore the legend in every field of life. He was suffering from bipolar disorder. In the last days when he gets up in the morning, his fingers were shivering due to the fear/shame of lacking money. In May 2017, He borrowed 25000 PKR just to pay the rent of his apartment. Last night in EDHI, his dead body was lying just in one trouser and their was no one even to receive/honor him. Yes this is Pakistan and this is our way of paying tribute to our legends. Shame on us!!!
